  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 9th level in warlock, your patron bestows upon you the key to unlock superior magical prowess at the cost of your own vitality.</p><p>You can perform an 1-hour ritual, which can be done over a short rest, to gain an additional warlock pact magic spell slot. When you use this feature, your maximum hit points are reduced by an amount equal to five times the level of the spell slot to a maximum of 5th level. The spell slot granted by this feature may only be used once, you do not regain it after a short rest.</p><p>If the spell slot is not used, the spell slot is lost after a long rest. Your current and maximum hit points are restored after a long rest. You may use this feature once per long rest.</p>",
